column5: Hey all  PLEASE can anyone provide conditions on the ramp, and the lower river.  I have a couple of friends coming down that want to go out.  Its a long run down there  Thanks

Haven't been down to the ramp - but most of this area is under 2 feet of snow! - Can't see it being accessable without some major hand work. The main roads are fine but the side streets are now starting to be plowed - don't think I would want to try the hill down to the launch!   Sorry to rain ( well - snow! ) on your parade but its better to know the facts   Don
the river is also full of huge chunks of ice floating down..
